name: 凯莉·妮科尔·佩克
name_full: 凯莉·妮科尔·佩克 Kylee Nicole Peck
introduction: Kylee Nicole Peck Is an American actress, writer, and director, producer located in St. Petersburg, FL. She was born December 03, 1991 in Newark, Ohio. Kylee Nicole began her career as an actress in 2021. She is represented by Beyond Beauty Talent. In her free time she enjoys gymnastics, cheerleading, tumbling, reading, writing, the Japanese language, learning, participating in sports, photography, comedy, editing, modeling, aviation, and community service.
